Mikhail Litvin, a Russian vlogger, blew up a BMW M5 worth about
R2 million. In the video, it shows the destruction
of Litvin's car was which went viral on social media. The video had
over 3.7 million views on YouTube in less than a day after it was published. The vlogger doused the car in petrol before shooting a
burning arrow at it with a bow. The German car was completely destroyed. 